WEBVTT

00:02.960 --> 00:08.680
<font color="#00ffff">I was awarded an income of Â£50,000</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a year. Albert will be expecting</font>
<font color="#00ffff">nothing less.</font>

00:08.720 --> 00:11.000
Â£20,000 a year!

00:11.040 --> 00:14.360
<font color="#ffff00">ELIZA: I think of you in the palace.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">That should have been my life.</font>

00:14.400 --> 00:16.280
<font color="#00ff00">The girls here are too delicious.</font>

00:16.320 --> 00:20.880
<font color="#ffff00">Please understand that all I've</font>
<font color="#ffff00">asked for is so that I can have</font>
<font color="#ffff00">my own position, my own freedom.</font>

00:20.920 --> 00:23.920
When I marry you tomorrow, it will be
as an ordinary woman.

00:23.960 --> 00:25.680
You will be my husband.

00:25.720 --> 00:27.400
<font color="#ffff00">And you will be my wife.</font>

00:28.400 --> 00:33.680
# Gloriana

00:34.680 --> 00:39.840
# Hallelujah

00:40.880 --> 00:46.640
# Gloriana

00:47.280 --> 00:52.440
# Hallelujah

00:53.440 --> 00:59.760
# Gloriana, hallelujah

00:59.800 --> 01:06.520
# Hallelujah! #

01:08.400 --> 01:10.400
(Birdsong)

01:18.440 --> 01:20.440
<font color="#ffff00">My Victoria.</font>

01:22.000 --> 01:28.074
