contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:41.560 --> 01:44.080
<font color="#00ff00">Majesty, I have a list</font>
<font color="#00ff00">for the dinner this...</font>

01:46.320 --> 01:49.240
<font color="#00ff00">Excuse me, Majesty.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I thought you were alone.</font>

01:50.360 --> 01:52.360
<font color="#00ff00">Your Highness.</font>

01:54.480 --> 01:56.880
<font color="#ffff00">She can just...walk in?</font>

01:58.520 --> 02:01.520
Her bedroom is next door.

02:01.560 --> 02:05.280
I like to have her near me,
in case I need anything in the night.

02:05.320 --> 02:07.280
<font color="#ffff00">But now you have me.</font>

02:13.280 --> 02:15.080
FRANCATELLI: Not much of a honeymoon.

02:15.120 --> 02:17.240
Two days at the Castle
and parties every night.

02:17.280 --> 02:19.520
I hope the Prince had time
to do his duty.

02:19.560 --> 02:23.160
<font color="#00ff00">The royal stallion needs time</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to cover his mare.</font>

02:23.760 --> 02:26.720
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, poor soul.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">What's the matter, Mrs Jenkins?</font>

02:26.760 --> 02:31.560
<font color="#ffff00">Mr Hedge, the whalebone man,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">says he can't leave his house</font>

02:31.600 --> 02:34.000
<font color="#ffff00">because they have the fever</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in Seven Dials.</font>

02:36.240 --> 02:37.840
<font color="#00ff00">I blame the foreigners.</font>

02:37.880 --> 02:40.080
<font color="#00ff00">One day this city is going to burst.</font>

02:43.560 --> 02:45.600
<font color="#ffff00">Must we have a state dinner tonight?</font>

02:45.640 --> 02:48.120
<font color="#ffff00">We've only just come back</font>
<font color="#ffff00">from our honeymoon.</font>

02:48.160 --> 02:51.760
I want to show that you have right of
precedence over the rest of
my family.

02:51.800 --> 02:56.360
I mean, it's quite absurd you should
be forced to walk into dinner after
my uncles.

02:58.120 --> 03:01.040
Your place is by my side. <font color="#ffff00">I know.</font>

03:02.520 --> 03:05.200
<font color="#ffff00">But I do not know if your uncles</font>
<font color="#ffff00">would agree.</font>

03:06.200 --> 03:10.560
We must start as we mean to go on.
Together.

03:10.600 --> 03:13.320
<font color="#00ffff">(Man calling out)</font>
<font color="#ffff00">What's that noise?</font>

03:14.360 --> 03:17.200
That is the muffin man.
<font color="#ffff00">The muffin man?</font>

03:17.240 --> 03:18.400
The muffin man!

03:18.440 --> 03:20.920
He carries them all on a tray
balancing on his head.

03:22.640 --> 03:24.160
Three for a penny.

03:25.200 --> 03:28.480
<font color="#ffff00">You know, when the children come,</font>

03:28.520 --> 03:32.040
<font color="#ffff00">I think it would be nice to live</font>
<font color="#ffff00">far away from the city.</font>

03:34.200 --> 03:36.800
What children?
<font color="#ffff00">Our children.</font>

03:38.520 --> 03:41.920
<font color="#ffff00">It would make me so happy to have</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a real family.</font>

03:41.960 --> 03:44.960
Aren't you happy now, Albert?
<font color="#ffff00">Of course. But...</font>

03:45.000 --> 03:47.560
<font color="#ffff00">I so want to be a father.</font>

03:47.600 --> 03:52.400
<font color="#ffff00">And you'll make a wonderful mother.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">This...I know.</font>

03:53.720 --> 03:56.320
<font color="#ffff00">We will do better than our parents,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I think.</font>

03:58.800 --> 04:00.880
Childbirth is a dangerous business.

04:01.880 --> 04:04.280
Look what happened to
Princess Charlotte.

04:05.360 --> 04:08.320
<font color="#00ffff">Well, the Queen is back from her</font>
<font color="#00ffff">honeymoon.</font>

04:09.120 --> 04:12.520
Already? <font color="#00ffff">I've been summoned to the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Palace for dinner.</font>

04:12.560 --> 04:14.560
<font color="#00ffff">Funny, I...</font>

04:14.600 --> 04:18.880
<font color="#00ffff">I thought she blamed me over the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">business of the Prince's allowance.</font>

04:18.920 --> 04:23.560
The Queen blames the Tories for
everything, from ingrowing toenails
to cholera.

04:25.120 --> 04:28.800
But Melbourne can't govern the
country from Brocket Hall for ever.

04:28.840 --> 04:30.960
Her Majesty will have
to get used to us.

04:34.760 --> 04:37.840
<font color="#00ff00">The boxes are here, Majesty.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I won't be long, my angel.</font>

04:37.880 --> 04:40.000
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps I could be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of some assistance?</font>

04:40.040 --> 04:43.120
Oh, you would be bored to tears.
Wouldn't he, Lehzen?

04:43.160 --> 04:45.120
Why don't you play something
on the piano?

04:45.160 --> 04:47.160
I can hear you from my desk.

04:49.320 --> 04:51.440
(DRAMATIC PIANO INTRO)

04:58.600 --> 05:00.760
<font color="#00ffff">Morning, Your Royal Highness.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Anson.</font>

05:00.800 --> 05:04.360
<font color="#00ffff">Perhaps, sir, you would like to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">acknowledge some of the wedding</font>
<font color="#00ffff">presents.</font>

05:04.400 --> 05:06.600
<font color="#00ffff">I have a list.</font>

05:06.640 --> 05:11.080
<font color="#ffff00">An embossed silver tureen</font>
<font color="#ffff00">from the Lord Mayor of Ly-cester.</font>

05:11.120 --> 05:13.120
<font color="#00ffff">We usually say Leicester, sir.</font>

05:27.160 --> 05:29.160
(Low chatter)

05:37.440 --> 05:39.960
Have you finished, sir?

05:43.880 --> 05:45.920
If only my neck were really
so swanlike.

05:45.960 --> 05:49.760
<font color="#00ff00">But I think my drawing is quite</font>
<font color="#00ff00">lifelike. Don't you agree,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Lord Alfred?</font>

05:49.800 --> 05:51.120
<font color="#00ffff">Mm.</font>

05:51.160 --> 05:53.960
<font color="#00ffff">I think, sir,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you have drawn what you see.</font>

06:15.760 --> 06:20.080
<font color="#00ff00">Your Royal Highness, the Queen is</font>
<font color="#00ff00">asking for you, sir.</font>

06:20.120 --> 06:22.200
<font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font>

06:22.240 --> 06:25.080
I was missing you so I wondered if
you could help me.

06:25.120 --> 06:27.280
<font color="#ffff00">I am at your service.</font>

06:30.800 --> 06:32.800
I have all these papers to sign.

06:36.240 --> 06:38.320
Oh, no, you don't have to read them.

06:38.360 --> 06:40.000
I've done that already.

06:40.880 --> 06:42.560
Here.

06:42.600 --> 06:45.960
It will be so much faster if I sign
and you blot.

06:49.080 --> 06:50.520
<font color="#ffff00">How delightful.</font>

06:50.560 --> 06:52.560
(Horse neighs and blows)

06:56.640 --> 06:58.640
<font color="#ffff00">Allow me.</font>

07:08.000 --> 07:12.000
Remember, the plan tonight is that
you will take me into dinner.

07:12.920 --> 07:15.560
<font color="#ffff00">Let's hope so.</font>

07:38.480 --> 07:40.480
(Lively chatter from behind doors)

07:52.280 --> 07:55.200
<font color="#00ff00">Her Majesty the Queen...</font>

07:55.240 --> 07:58.440
<font color="#00ff00">and His Royal Highness</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Prince Albert.</font>

08:08.120 --> 08:14.560
<font color="#00ff00">His Royal Highness</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the Duke of Sussex and</font>
<font color="#00ff00">His Grace the Duke of Wellington.</font>

08:19.080 --> 08:20.480
Uncle Sussex.

08:25.320 --> 08:28.560
<font color="#00ffff">Your honeymoon was not a long</font>
<font color="#00ffff">campaign, Ma'am.</font>

08:28.600 --> 08:33.400
Why, Duke, I don't regard marriage
as a battlefield.

08:33.440 --> 08:35.440
<font color="#00ffff">Perhaps that comes later, Ma'am.</font>

08:37.600 --> 08:43.240
<font color="#ffff00">I don't know if you are aware, sir,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">but I believe we are related</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on your side of the family,</font>

08:43.280 --> 08:45.480
<font color="#ffff00">through your mother.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Indeed?</font>

08:45.520 --> 08:49.320
<font color="#00ff00">I don't know how you Germans keep</font>
<font color="#00ff00">track of all your principalities.</font>

08:50.560 --> 08:55.280
<font color="#00ff00">At least here we only have</font>
<font color="#00ff00">one royal family.</font>

08:56.200 --> 09:00.080
Dear Mr Bumps! How I have missed him,
Lord Alfred.

09:00.120 --> 09:02.680
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Bumps, please curtsey</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to your Queen.</font>

09:03.840 --> 09:06.120
(Gasping and giggling)

09:06.160 --> 09:08.800
Oh, how adorable! <font color="#00ffff">He's been</font>
<font color="#00ffff">practising all day.</font>

09:08.840 --> 09:12.280
<font color="#ffff00">The dog is wearing jewellery.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Is this an English custom?</font>

09:12.320 --> 09:15.720
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Bumps was so jealous of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">my miniature of Her Majesty</font>

09:15.760 --> 09:18.120
<font color="#00ffff">that he wouldn't let me alone</font>
<font color="#00ffff">till I got him one too.</font>

09:19.360 --> 09:20.840
(Mr Bumps whines)

09:21.560 --> 09:23.440
<font color="#00ffff">Ma'am.</font>

09:23.480 --> 09:26.080
<font color="#ffff00">The dogs wear jewellery,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the pianos are out of tune</font>

09:26.120 --> 09:28.440
<font color="#ffff00">and all the people talk about is</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the weather.</font>

09:28.480 --> 09:30.840
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, well, I think there are</font>
<font color="#00ff00">some consolations.</font>

09:36.000 --> 09:38.000
Albert?

09:41.120 --> 09:43.160
<font color="#00ff00">As the only prince</font>
<font color="#00ff00">of the blood present,</font>

09:43.200 --> 09:46.400
<font color="#00ff00">I believe it is my privilege</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to take you into dinner, Ma'am.</font>

09:46.440 --> 09:51.480
Albert is my husband and should be
by my side. It is time things were
changed.

09:51.520 --> 09:53.200
<font color="#00ff00">Before you came to the throne,</font>

09:53.240 --> 09:56.240
<font color="#00ff00">there were many people in this</font>
<font color="#00ff00">country who thought that a system</font>

09:56.280 --> 10:00.680
<font color="#00ff00">that allowed a young, inexperienced</font>
<font color="#00ff00">girl to take the throne</font>

10:00.720 --> 10:04.040
<font color="#00ff00">over a man like my brother</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Cumberland should be changed.</font>

10:04.080 --> 10:06.040
<font color="#00ff00">I was not among them, Ma'am.</font>

10:06.080 --> 10:11.800
<font color="#00ff00">But then I do not believe that rules</font>
<font color="#00ff00">should be altered when they become</font>
<font color="#00ff00">inconvenient.</font>

10:32.920 --> 10:35.040
<font color="#00ff00">You've done your hair differently,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Duchess.</font>

10:35.080 --> 10:37.080
<font color="#00ff00">It brings out the curve</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in your neck.</font>

10:37.120 --> 10:41.680
<font color="#ffff00">Don't worry, Albert. They will not</font>
<font color="#ffff00">treat you like this when you have</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a son.</font>

10:41.720 --> 10:43.720
<font color="#ffff00">Then they will all respect you.</font>

11:01.080 --> 11:04.440
I won't give up.
You belong at my side.

11:05.520 --> 11:07.840
<font color="#ffff00">There is no place for me here...</font>

11:09.440 --> 11:12.280
<font color="#ffff00">..here among your curtseying dogs.</font>

11:13.080 --> 11:14.880
(Whispers) Yes!

11:16.040 --> 11:17.640
Yes, there is.

11:17.680 --> 11:20.000
This is your home, Albert.

11:30.880 --> 11:32.880
(Dramatic piano music)

11:58.480 --> 12:00.560
<font color="#ffff00">I can do nothing right.</font>

12:00.600 --> 12:03.760
<font color="#00ff00">Nonsense. You have a happy marriage.</font>

12:03.800 --> 12:06.240
<font color="#00ff00">Who in our family can say that?</font>

12:06.280 --> 12:08.640
<font color="#00ff00">You have always been too sensitive.</font>

12:09.760 --> 12:13.520
<font color="#00ff00">Ignore them and concentrate on</font>
<font color="#00ff00">producing an heir.</font>

12:13.560 --> 12:17.480
<font color="#00ff00">Once you have done that...</font>
<font color="#00ff00">everything will be different.</font>

12:17.520 --> 12:19.280
<font color="#ffff00">That is what everyone says but...</font>

12:20.280 --> 12:22.800
<font color="#ffff00">..it's not as easy as it seems.</font>

12:24.240 --> 12:27.320
<font color="#ffff00">I have to find a place for myself.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Ah!</font>

12:27.360 --> 12:29.480
<font color="#00ff00">Next to your wife</font>
<font color="#00ff00">when you go into dinner?</font>

12:29.520 --> 12:31.080
<font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

12:33.680 --> 12:35.520
<font color="#ffff00">A place I have earned.</font>

12:35.560 --> 12:38.320
I can't bear to see the Prince
so humiliated.

12:38.360 --> 12:40.440
I'm surprised Uncle Sussex does not
see that.

12:40.480 --> 12:43.480
<font color="#ffff00">The Duke of Sussex is most singular.</font>

12:44.840 --> 12:49.320
<font color="#ffff00">I have never seen him without the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">skull cap and I believe he lives off</font>
<font color="#ffff00">ices and turtle soup.</font>

12:50.280 --> 12:53.160
I suppose he has a mistress,
like all my other uncles.

12:53.200 --> 12:57.240
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, no, Ma'am. No, he is happily</font>
<font color="#ffff00">married to Lady Cecilia Buggin.</font>

12:57.280 --> 13:01.080
<font color="#ffff00">But because she is not of royal</font>
<font color="#ffff00">blood, she is not recognised</font>
<font color="#ffff00">as his wife</font>

13:01.120 --> 13:03.000
<font color="#ffff00">under the Royal Marriages Act.</font>

13:04.000 --> 13:06.000
If only Lord M were here.

13:06.040 --> 13:08.040
What would he do?

13:09.520 --> 13:11.520
<font color="#ffff00">Poor Mr Hedge.</font>

13:12.640 --> 13:14.400
<font color="#00ffff">What kind of fever is it?</font>

13:14.440 --> 13:16.440
<font color="#ffff00">Indian cholera, most like.</font>

13:18.560 --> 13:23.840
<font color="#ffff00">Slums like Seven Dials, you can't</font>
<font color="#ffff00">see it, but it's there, hanging in</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the air.</font>

13:28.920 --> 13:30.920
<font color="#ffff00">Don't worry, we're quite safe here.</font>

14:03.200 --> 14:07.400
<font color="#00ff00">Your Royal Highness, the Queen has</font>
<font color="#00ff00">requested that you join her in the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Throne Room</font>

14:07.440 --> 14:12.880
<font color="#00ff00">for an audience with Mr Allen and</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Mr Buxton of the British And Foreign</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Anti-Slavery Society.</font>

14:12.920 --> 14:16.080
<font color="#00ffff">As you know, Your Majesty,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the wicked practice of slavery</font>

14:16.120 --> 14:20.280
<font color="#00ffff">has been abolished throughout</font>
<font color="#00ffff">your dominions, yet it continues</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in other...</font>

14:21.280 --> 14:23.840
<font color="#00ffff">..less enlightened nations,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">most notably America.</font>

14:25.200 --> 14:27.600
<font color="#00ffff">We have organised a convention,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Ma'am,</font>

14:27.640 --> 14:30.120
<font color="#00ffff">to include like-minded people</font>
<font color="#00ffff">from around the world</font>

14:30.160 --> 14:34.240
<font color="#00ffff">to protest against the continuation</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of this barbarity.</font>

14:34.280 --> 14:37.680
<font color="#00ffff">There will be a delegation of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">American abolitionists</font>

14:37.720 --> 14:40.920
<font color="#00ffff">that will include some Negro slaves</font>
<font color="#00ffff">that have escaped their bonds.</font>

14:40.960 --> 14:43.120
A worthy endeavour, gentlemen.

14:44.160 --> 14:46.040
How can I assist you?

14:47.960 --> 14:52.120
<font color="#00ffff">We wondered, Ma'am, whether you</font>
<font color="#00ffff">would open the proceedings.</font>

14:52.160 --> 14:55.800
<font color="#00ffff">To have your public support would be</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of inestimable value.</font>

14:55.840 --> 14:57.800
<font color="#00ffff">We have many distinguished</font>
<font color="#00ffff">supporters.</font>

14:57.840 --> 15:01.320
<font color="#00ffff">Sir Robert Peel has been tireless</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in his efforts,</font>

15:01.360 --> 15:04.600
<font color="#00ffff">but...there is no greater ally</font>
<font color="#00ffff">than yourself.</font>

15:04.640 --> 15:08.920
<font color="#ffff00">I find it shocking that this</font>
<font color="#ffff00">practice should continue</font>
<font color="#ffff00">across the Atlantic</font>

15:08.960 --> 15:12.520
<font color="#ffff00">in the country known as "the land of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the free". </font><font color="#00ffff"> Indeed, sir.</font>

15:12.560 --> 15:16.840
I have been a supporter of your cause
ever since I was a little girl...

15:16.880 --> 15:19.360
and I shall certainly make
a subscription.

15:21.120 --> 15:23.160
However...

15:23.200 --> 15:26.200
as your sovereign,
I cannot open your meeting...

15:28.000 --> 15:30.280
..however much I might want to.

15:35.760 --> 15:38.160
(Bell tolling in distance)
(Coughing)

15:46.280 --> 15:48.280
<font color="#00ffff">(Coughs)</font>

15:57.320 --> 15:59.320
(Man retches)

16:06.520 --> 16:08.160
<font color="#ffff00">You can't come down here, miss.</font>

16:08.200 --> 16:10.720
<font color="#ffff00">By order of the Parish Council,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on account of the fever.</font>

16:10.760 --> 16:15.400
<font color="#00ffff">My cousin and her baby live down</font>
<font color="#00ffff">there. They need my help.</font>

16:15.440 --> 16:18.520
<font color="#ffff00">If I let you in, miss,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I can't let you out.</font>

16:18.560 --> 16:22.000
<font color="#ffff00">So, you should decide how urgent</font>
<font color="#ffff00">your business is.</font>

16:29.120 --> 16:31.120
My angel.

16:51.720 --> 16:53.720
Lehzen.

16:54.840 --> 16:56.960
<font color="#00ff00">Yes, Majesty.</font>

16:58.560 --> 17:00.560
I need to ask you something.

17:03.720 --> 17:05.720
<font color="#00ff00">Of course.</font>

17:12.119 --> 17:14.119
(Clears throat)

17:16.440 --> 17:18.960
Now that I'm married
there will be changes.

17:19.000 --> 17:23.200
<font color="#00ff00">Yes, Majesty. </font><font color="#ffffff"> But I don't want</font>
any changes just yet.

17:23.240 --> 17:24.800
<font color="#00ff00">No, Majesty.</font>

17:25.640 --> 17:27.400
I was wondering...

17:27.440 --> 17:33.040
if I wanted things to stay...just as
they are for perhaps a year or so...

17:35.400 --> 17:36.880
..how I might do that.

17:42.200 --> 17:44.480
I keep thinking about
poor Princess Charlotte.

17:44.520 --> 17:46.320
<font color="#00ff00">Oh.</font>

17:46.360 --> 17:49.840
<font color="#00ff00">Of course, Majesty. I am</font>
<font color="#00ff00">inexperienced in these matters.</font>

17:49.880 --> 17:51.720
Of course.

17:51.760 --> 17:55.080
<font color="#00ff00">But my sister's married</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and she writes to me very frankly.</font>

17:57.200 --> 17:59.200
<font color="#00ff00">(Whispers)</font>

18:05.480 --> 18:07.480
Ten times?

18:09.800 --> 18:13.440
<font color="#00ffff">We would be most honoured by your</font>
<font color="#00ffff">presence, Your Royal Highness.</font>

18:13.480 --> 18:17.720
<font color="#ffff00">Victoria, I have decided to attend</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the Anti-Slavery convention.</font>

18:17.760 --> 18:20.800
<font color="#ffff00">And I hope to say a few words</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of my own.</font>

18:20.840 --> 18:23.160
<font color="#00ffff">And it will be a great honour, sir.</font>

18:27.480 --> 18:29.640
You are going to make a speech?

18:29.680 --> 18:32.880
<font color="#ffff00">It is a subject about which I feel</font>
<font color="#ffff00">very strongly, meine Liebe,</font>

18:32.920 --> 18:37.960
<font color="#ffff00">and...the usual protocols</font>
<font color="#ffff00">which prevent you from attending</font>
<font color="#ffff00">do not apply to me.</font>

18:39.720 --> 18:41.960
<font color="#ffff00">I need a position, Victoria.</font>

18:50.200 --> 18:52.480
<font color="#00ffff">Are you following me?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">You're not meant to be here.</font>

18:52.520 --> 18:55.960
I know you went to Seven Dials and I
know you found it closed to visitors.

18:56.000 --> 18:57.120
<font color="#00ffff">How?</font>

18:57.160 --> 18:59.880
A chef has a nose for the most
interesting ingredients.

18:59.920 --> 19:04.480
The thing is, Miss Skerrett,
I have friends in Seven Dials.

19:04.520 --> 19:07.000
Friends who do not let the Peelers
stand in their way.

19:07.040 --> 19:10.520
Is there something I can do for you?

19:11.400 --> 19:13.400
<font color="#00ffff">I don't know. What's in it for you?</font>

19:14.120 --> 19:16.120
I can think of something.

19:19.760 --> 19:23.840
<font color="#ffff00">I have written what I wish to say</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in German but I must deliver it</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in English, of course.</font>

19:23.880 --> 19:25.800
<font color="#ffff00">Also, I believe it may be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">rather too long.</font>

19:25.840 --> 19:28.600
<font color="#00ffff">I think if you were proposing</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to publish an essay, sir...</font>

19:28.640 --> 19:34.120
<font color="#00ffff">Would you erm...like me to abridge</font>
<font color="#00ffff">it for you, sir, and...put it into</font>
<font color="#00ffff">English?</font>

19:34.160 --> 19:37.840
<font color="#ffff00">I would be most grateful.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Your German is far superior</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to my English.</font>

19:37.880 --> 19:40.680
<font color="#00ffff">It's a very brave undertaking,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">if I may say so, sir.</font>

19:40.720 --> 19:44.200
<font color="#ffff00">You think I'm foolhardy? I see.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">But ever since I arrived</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in this country,</font>

19:44.240 --> 19:47.200
<font color="#ffff00">I have been judged by people who</font>
<font color="#ffff00">know nothing of my true character.</font>

19:47.240 --> 19:49.680
<font color="#ffff00">They laugh at my clothes,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">they sneer at my accent.</font>

19:49.720 --> 19:51.880
<font color="#ffff00">I have seen cartoons when I am drawn</font>
<font color="#ffff00">as a sausage.</font>

19:51.920 --> 19:56.120
<font color="#ffff00">So I have decided if I am to be held</font>
<font color="#ffff00">up to scrutiny, it should be for</font>
<font color="#ffff00">something I believe in.</font>

19:57.120 --> 20:01.000
<font color="#ffff00">What is it that Shakespeare says?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">"Cowards die many times before</font>
<font color="#ffff00">their deaths."</font>

20:01.040 --> 20:05.720
<font color="#00ffff">"The valiant never taste of death</font>
<font color="#00ffff">but once." Julius Caesar.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Act Two, Scene Two.</font>

20:05.760 --> 20:07.400
<font color="#ffff00">Ha.</font>

20:11.600 --> 20:15.680
<font color="#ffff00">This bar-bar-ous trade is repugnant</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to Christianity</font>

20:15.720 --> 20:18.800
<font color="#ffff00">and the blackest stain</font>
<font color="#ffff00">upon civilised...</font>

20:27.120 --> 20:29.240
You don't have to make a speech.

20:29.280 --> 20:31.920
<font color="#ffff00">I have to earn my position.</font>

20:34.080 --> 20:36.080
And as to your position...

20:36.120 --> 20:39.320
I may have a solution to that.

20:39.360 --> 20:41.360
But you'll have to wait and see.

20:42.680 --> 20:46.000
<font color="#ffff00">I can make you tell me, you know.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I'd like to see you try!</font>

20:48.280 --> 20:49.760
<font color="#ffff00">Tell me.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">No.</font>

20:49.800 --> 20:51.800
<font color="#ffff00">Tell me.</font>

21:31.560 --> 21:34.520
One, two, three, four, five,

21:34.560 --> 21:37.520
six, seven, eight, nine, ten.

21:48.840 --> 21:51.320
<font color="#00ffff">His Royal Highness,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the Duke of Sussex.</font>

21:51.360 --> 21:53.360
Uncle.

21:55.080 --> 21:58.160
I asked you here today because there
is something I wish to discuss.

21:58.200 --> 22:01.600
<font color="#00ff00">It's no use, Victoria. I am not</font>
<font color="#00ff00">going to change my mind.</font>

22:04.040 --> 22:07.560
<font color="#00ff00">Lord knows...my life has not been</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a happy one...</font>

22:08.600 --> 22:12.720
<font color="#00ff00">..but I am the son of a King and</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I will not give up my birthright.</font>

22:12.760 --> 22:15.280
I want to talk to you
about your wife, Uncle.

22:16.000 --> 22:18.000
<font color="#00ff00">You want to talk about Cecilia?</font>

22:19.000 --> 22:21.320
<font color="#00ff00">If you are going to tell me</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that my marriage is illegal</font>

22:21.360 --> 22:26.840
<font color="#00ff00">because I did not have the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">sovereign's consent, then I believe</font>
<font color="#00ff00">you are nine years too late.</font>

22:27.960 --> 22:32.440
I was thinking... I should like
to meet your wife.

22:32.480 --> 22:34.480
<font color="#00ff00">You would?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Yes.</font>

22:35.480 --> 22:39.560
Yes, because I feel it is important
that spouses are given the respect
they are due.

22:39.600 --> 22:41.880
<font color="#00ff00">That is most gracious, Ma'am.</font>

22:42.880 --> 22:46.600
<font color="#00ff00">But I'm afraid it will not change my</font>
<font color="#00ff00">mind in the question of precedence.</font>

22:46.640 --> 22:50.240
Of course, if she were to be received
at court, she would need a title.

22:50.280 --> 22:53.800
As your marriage is morganatic,
she cannot be Duchess of Sussex,

22:53.840 --> 22:58.960
but I think she could perhaps be
a Duchess of say...Inverness?

23:01.440 --> 23:03.720
<font color="#00ff00">Duchess of Inverness.</font>

23:06.320 --> 23:09.800
Yes. It is one of the Sovereign's
discretionary titles.

23:10.840 --> 23:14.160
So, Uncle, do you think your wife
could be agreeable?

23:16.160 --> 23:19.520
<font color="#00ff00">To be received at Court</font>
<font color="#00ff00">as a Duchess?</font>

23:21.680 --> 23:24.080
<font color="#00ff00">Yes, I believe she would.</font>

23:24.120 --> 23:27.320
Of course, the circumstances
would have to be right.

23:28.360 --> 23:30.720
<font color="#00ff00">My wife's happiness is everything</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to me.</font>

23:32.720 --> 23:34.720
I feel the same about Albert.

23:52.360 --> 23:54.600
<font color="#00ff00">Never mind, Duchess.</font>

23:54.640 --> 23:56.880
<font color="#00ff00">Not all your arrows</font>
<font color="#00ff00">miss their target.</font>

23:57.880 --> 23:59.880
You and the Prince are so different.

24:02.160 --> 24:04.920
<font color="#00ff00">Perhaps I could help you</font>
<font color="#00ff00">with your aim, Duchess.</font>

24:08.360 --> 24:10.040
<font color="#00ff00">Straighter.</font>

24:10.880 --> 24:12.880
<font color="#00ff00">And your hips.</font>

24:16.480 --> 24:18.400
<font color="#00ff00">Hold it.</font>

24:21.440 --> 24:23.520
Oh, doesn't Harriet look charming?

24:23.560 --> 24:28.720
So kind of her to stay in town with
me, whilst her husband has gone back
to Ragsby.

24:28.760 --> 24:30.760
<font color="#ffff00">Indeed.</font>

24:37.040 --> 24:39.120
<font color="#00ff00">When our mother left...</font>

24:41.960 --> 24:43.960
<font color="#00ff00">..Albi tried so hard not to cry.</font>

24:45.000 --> 24:47.640
<font color="#00ff00">I always wanted to be there</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to protect him.</font>

24:47.680 --> 24:50.840
He was lucky to have you.
<font color="#00ff00">No, I was the lucky one.</font>

24:50.880 --> 24:52.760
<font color="#00ff00">He is my better half, I think.</font>

24:52.800 --> 24:54.640
And is your other half so very bad?

24:54.680 --> 24:56.880
<font color="#00ff00">What do you think, Duchess?</font>

24:56.920 --> 25:01.280
I think, sir, that...you are a sheep
in wolf's clothing.

25:01.320 --> 25:03.680
You pretend to be what my mother
would call a rake,

25:03.720 --> 25:07.400
but underneath...I think you have
a heart that is tender.

25:08.840 --> 25:12.320
<font color="#00ff00">I think...that you flatter me,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Duchess.</font>

25:12.360 --> 25:16.080
No, sir. I just describe what I see.

25:17.040 --> 25:20.760
<font color="#ffff00">As President of the British And</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Foreign Anti-Slavery Society,</font>

25:20.800 --> 25:24.200
<font color="#ffff00">I am glad so many people are here.</font>

25:24.240 --> 25:28.040
<font color="#ffff00">This bar-bar-ous trade is repugnant</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to the spirit of Christianity.</font>

25:28.080 --> 25:31.560
<font color="#00ffff">Barbarous, sir, is the correct</font>
<font color="#00ffff">pronunciation. </font><font color="#ffff00"> Thank you.</font>

25:31.600 --> 25:36.880
<font color="#ffff00">This...barbarous trade is repugnant</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to the spirit of Christianity</font>

25:36.920 --> 25:40.240
<font color="#ffff00">and the blackest stain upon</font>
<font color="#ffff00">civilised Europe. </font><font color="#00ffff"> Very good, sir.</font>

25:40.280 --> 25:42.920
<font color="#00ffff">And erm...remember you must...</font>
<font color="#00ffff">speak up.</font>

25:42.960 --> 25:44.840
<font color="#00ffff">Exeter Hall is a large venue,</font>

25:44.880 --> 25:47.560
<font color="#00ffff">and I believe they're expecting more</font>
<font color="#00ffff">than 3,000 people.</font>

25:47.600 --> 25:48.840
<font color="#ffff00">So many?</font>

25:48.880 --> 25:52.960
<font color="#00ffff">It is a cause that has great support</font>
<font color="#00ffff">here across all parties and</font>
<font color="#00ffff">interests.</font>

25:53.000 --> 25:55.000
<font color="#00ffff">It's not often that you find</font>
<font color="#00ffff">such accord.</font>

25:55.040 --> 25:58.880
<font color="#00ffff">I believe that not only will Lord</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Palmerston, the Foreign Secretary,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">be attending,</font>

25:58.920 --> 26:02.560
<font color="#00ffff">but also Sir Robert Peel,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">who as you know, sir, is a Tory.</font>

26:02.600 --> 26:07.280
<font color="#ffff00">Though I believe he was instrumental</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in reducing my allowance by 20,000.</font>

26:08.480 --> 26:11.040
<font color="#ffff00">Victoria does not like him.</font>

26:11.080 --> 26:14.000
<font color="#00ffff">Sir Robert Peel will be</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Prime Minister one day.</font>

26:14.040 --> 26:16.840
<font color="#ffff00">And you believe she should overcome</font>
<font color="#ffff00">her dislike.</font>

26:19.560 --> 26:20.840
<font color="#ffff00">I see.</font>

26:34.600 --> 26:36.600
(Drunken muttering)

26:46.520 --> 26:49.920
Think you can run faster
than the constable? <font color="#00ffff">Yeah!</font>

26:49.960 --> 26:52.440
Hey, stop, you little thief!

26:52.480 --> 26:54.480
<font color="#ffff00">Come back here, you little rascal!</font>

27:13.520 --> 27:15.520
(Coughing)

27:25.600 --> 27:27.600
(Baby wails)

27:29.280 --> 27:30.720
(Knocks on door)

27:30.760 --> 27:33.600
<font color="#00ff00">Nein. Nein. Bringt eine andere.</font>

27:33.640 --> 27:35.360
<font color="#00ff00">Exactly the man I would like to see.</font>

27:35.400 --> 27:37.760
<font color="#00ff00">Which necktie do you prefer?</font>

27:37.800 --> 27:40.720
<font color="#00ff00">I would like to look</font>
<font color="#00ff00">my best tonight.</font>

27:40.760 --> 27:42.760
<font color="#ffff00">(Speaks German)</font>

27:51.240 --> 27:54.360
<font color="#ffff00">I saw you today</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with the Duchess of Sutherland.</font>

27:54.400 --> 27:57.120
<font color="#00ff00">Yes, she is a keen toxophilite.</font>

27:59.320 --> 28:01.600
<font color="#ffff00">She's a married woman, Ernest.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I know.</font>

28:01.640 --> 28:04.000
<font color="#ffff00">Even Papa does not seduce</font>
<font color="#ffff00">other men's wives.</font>

28:04.040 --> 28:07.320
<font color="#00ff00">No. But I don't think Papa has ever</font>
<font color="#00ff00">fallen in love either.</font>

28:09.800 --> 28:12.240
<font color="#ffff00">I think it would be best</font>
<font color="#ffff00">if you went back to Coburg.</font>

28:13.920 --> 28:15.920
<font color="#00ff00">Well, I would like to stay...</font>

28:17.440 --> 28:20.360
<font color="#00ff00">..for your speech,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to give you my support.</font>

28:20.400 --> 28:22.800
<font color="#ffff00">At the moment,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I don't know if I can...</font>

28:22.840 --> 28:26.360
<font color="#ffff00">Well, you should go home.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I must face this alone.</font>

28:26.400 --> 28:27.720
<font color="#00ff00">Ja.</font>

28:27.760 --> 28:29.760
<font color="#00ff00">But you are not alone, are you?</font>

28:42.040 --> 28:44.040
(Coughing nearby)

28:45.040 --> 28:46.840
Mrs Ashdown?

28:46.880 --> 28:50.240
My name is Charles Francatelli.
I'm a...friend of Miss Skerrett's.

28:50.280 --> 28:52.080
She asked me to give you this.

28:52.120 --> 28:53.360
<font color="#00ff00">(Child coughs)</font>

28:53.400 --> 28:55.520
<font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font>

28:55.560 --> 28:58.400
May I come in?
<font color="#ffff00">You shouldn't. It's not safe.</font>

28:58.440 --> 29:00.360
I brought protection.

29:00.400 --> 29:01.920
80 per cent proof.

29:03.720 --> 29:06.720
<font color="#ffff00">You're braver than the doctor.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">He won't come down here.</font>

29:07.840 --> 29:10.680
For the baby?
<font color="#ffff00">She won't stop coughing.</font>

29:10.720 --> 29:14.120
<font color="#ffff00">I've been so worried.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Chin up, hey?</font>

29:15.520 --> 29:17.520
<font color="#00ff00">(Child coughs)</font>

29:19.080 --> 29:21.200
Maybe I can help.
<font color="#ffff00">Why would you help me?</font>

29:22.280 --> 29:24.560
<font color="#ffff00">We don't know each other.</font>

29:24.600 --> 29:26.600
I know Miss Skerrett.

29:27.920 --> 29:30.600
I know how much
she worries about you.

29:30.640 --> 29:32.640
<font color="#ffff00">You must like her very much.</font>

29:34.720 --> 29:37.600
<font color="#00ff00">His Grace, the Duke of Wellington.</font>

29:39.200 --> 29:45.480
<font color="#00ff00">Her Majesty, the Queen, and</font>
<font color="#00ff00">His Royal Highness, Prince Albert.</font>

29:45.520 --> 29:47.720
<font color="#ffff00">I shall miss you, my dear nephew.</font>

29:47.760 --> 29:49.920
<font color="#ffff00">But you will be back soon.</font>

29:49.960 --> 29:51.840
<font color="#ffff00">A christening, perhaps.</font>

29:51.880 --> 29:53.360
<font color="#00ff00">Perhaps.</font>

30:00.280 --> 30:03.200
<font color="#00ffff">Good evening, Your Royal Highness.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Lady Cecilia.</font>

30:03.240 --> 30:08.400
<font color="#00ff00">Actually, Wellington, my wife is now</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Duchess of Inverness.</font>

30:08.440 --> 30:10.560
<font color="#00ffff">A discretionary title?</font>

30:11.240 --> 30:13.960
<font color="#00ffff">The Queen has deployed her arsenal.</font>

30:14.000 --> 30:16.160
<font color="#00ffff">My congratulations, Duchess.</font>

30:16.200 --> 30:18.240
<font color="#ffff00">Duke.</font>

30:18.280 --> 30:24.400
<font color="#00ff00">His Royal Highness, the Duke of</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Sussex, Her Grace, the Duchess of</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Inverness.</font>

30:29.120 --> 30:31.120
Uncle Sussex.

30:32.320 --> 30:34.760
<font color="#00ff00">May I present my wife?</font>

30:35.880 --> 30:37.360
<font color="#ffff00">Your Majesty.</font>

30:38.560 --> 30:41.280
I am glad to meet you
at last...Duchess.

30:41.320 --> 30:43.840
<font color="#ffff00">Delighted to be here, Ma'am.</font>

31:00.880 --> 31:02.880
Shall we?

31:21.360 --> 31:24.840
<font color="#ffff00">Our little Queen has become rather</font>
<font color="#ffff00">good at getting what she wants.</font>

31:24.880 --> 31:27.240
<font color="#ffff00">Don't you think, Duke?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Women!</font>

31:29.880 --> 31:33.160
Did you see Wellington's face when
The Duke of Sussex gave way to you?

31:34.320 --> 31:36.720
Don't you think I've managed it
all rather neatly?

31:36.760 --> 31:39.240
<font color="#ffff00">I think the way you handled it was</font>
<font color="#ffff00">faultless.</font>

31:41.400 --> 31:42.840
<font color="#ffff00">You're extraordinary.</font>

31:42.880 --> 31:47.680
Albert, what's the matter? I thought
you would be pleased. We've won.

31:49.600 --> 31:53.960
<font color="#ffff00">I think this is your victory...</font>
<font color="#ffff00">not mine.</font>

31:56.760 --> 31:58.760
(Clock ticking)

32:09.520 --> 32:13.720
<font color="#00ff00">How splendid to be</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a king with 15 children.</font>

32:13.760 --> 32:15.760
Who went mad.
<font color="#00ff00">(Chuckles)</font>

32:17.400 --> 32:21.360
<font color="#00ff00">I think that my brother will have</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a very happy marriage.</font>

32:21.400 --> 32:24.680
Yes. He loves the Queen enough.

32:27.160 --> 32:30.320
<font color="#00ff00">But I do not think</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that I will be so lucky.</font>

32:31.240 --> 32:33.240
Truly happy marriages are rare.

32:34.400 --> 32:36.400
In my experience.

32:40.000 --> 32:43.360
<font color="#00ff00">I wanted to tell you that I will be</font>
<font color="#00ff00">going back to Coburg shortly.</font>

32:45.840 --> 32:49.160
<font color="#00ff00">Albert thinks that</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I will be safer there.</font>

32:49.200 --> 32:52.000
Safer? I hardly think
you're in much danger

32:52.040 --> 32:54.280
from a harmless flirtation
with a married woman.

32:54.320 --> 32:56.680
<font color="#00ff00">You think that this is harmless?</font>

32:56.720 --> 32:58.880
Don't you?
<font color="#00ff00">No.</font>

33:01.200 --> 33:03.200
Then I must wish you bon voyage.

33:43.280 --> 33:46.480
<font color="#ffff00">Promise me you will take care.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I will be fine, brother.</font>

33:51.080 --> 33:54.680
<font color="#00ff00">Just hurry up and produce a son</font>
<font color="#00ff00">so I may be a godfather, yeah.</font>

34:00.120 --> 34:02.120
<font color="#00ff00">Make sure you look after my brother.</font>

34:12.520 --> 34:14.520
<font color="#ffff00">(Whispers in German)</font>

34:16.639 --> 34:18.639
You will miss him very much?

34:31.400 --> 34:34.120
<font color="#ffff00">I hope you have enjoyed your stay,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">sir.</font>

34:34.159 --> 34:36.159
<font color="#00ff00">I will never forget it.</font>

34:58.000 --> 35:00.800
<font color="#ffff00">For 20 years, we've been together</font>
<font color="#ffff00">every day.</font>

35:00.840 --> 35:02.840
<font color="#ffff00">But now I have you...</font>

35:06.080 --> 35:08.320
<font color="#ffff00">..and soon we will have</font>
<font color="#ffff00">our own family.</font>

35:29.960 --> 35:31.960
<font color="#00ffff">Welcome to England, Mr Barrett.</font>

35:35.720 --> 35:37.800
(Low chatter)

35:40.960 --> 35:43.240
<font color="#00ffff">I just got a letter</font>
<font color="#00ffff">from Mrs Ashdown.</font>

35:56.600 --> 35:58.400
<font color="#00ffff">She's very happy</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in her new lodgings.</font>

35:58.440 --> 36:01.280
<font color="#00ffff">She asked me to tell you how</font>
<font color="#00ffff">grateful she is. </font><font color="#ffffff"> How's the baby?</font>

36:01.320 --> 36:06.520
<font color="#00ffff">Still has a cough but Mrs Ashdown</font>
<font color="#00ffff">thinks now they are out of the city,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">it will get better.</font>

36:06.560 --> 36:08.040
I'm glad.

36:09.040 --> 36:12.440
<font color="#00ffff">I used to fancy myself</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a good judge of men,</font>

36:13.600 --> 36:17.800
<font color="#00ffff">but I can't think of many people who</font>
<font color="#00ffff">would do what you did for a stranger</font>
<font color="#00ffff">so...</font>

36:20.360 --> 36:22.360
I didn't do it for her.

36:24.680 --> 36:26.960
<font color="#00ffff">I suppose you want something</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in return.</font>

36:28.720 --> 36:30.120
Yes.

36:31.200 --> 36:33.200
Yes, Miss Skerrett, I do.

36:38.880 --> 36:41.640
I find myself thinking about you
sometimes

36:41.680 --> 36:45.560
when I'm at my sugar work and I find
it hard to concentrate because...

36:46.840 --> 36:50.120
..I...don't know your name.

36:51.720 --> 36:54.640
Your real name, that is,
the name you were born with.

36:54.680 --> 36:56.680
So er...

36:57.680 --> 36:59.800
..that is what I would like.

37:02.760 --> 37:04.400
<font color="#00ffff">My name?</font>

37:07.560 --> 37:09.000
<font color="#00ffff">Nancy.</font>

37:11.440 --> 37:13.440
Thank you...

37:15.000 --> 37:17.000
..Nancy.

37:19.160 --> 37:25.080
Just...speak up and smile
occasionally.

37:25.120 --> 37:28.560
If I see you looking too stern
I shall make an objection.

37:30.840 --> 37:32.840
<font color="#ffff00">I shall be looking out for you.</font>

37:38.480 --> 37:41.000
Good luck.

37:42.120 --> 37:44.120
<font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font>

37:51.680 --> 37:54.760
<font color="#00ffff">The first time you speak, you should</font>
<font color="#00ffff">call him 'Your Royal Highness'.</font>

37:54.800 --> 37:56.800
<font color="#00ffff">After that, you can call him 'sir'.</font>

37:58.320 --> 38:02.520
Should I tell him he can call me
Jonas if he wants?

38:02.560 --> 38:05.840
<font color="#00ffff">It is usual not to speak to royalty</font>
<font color="#00ffff">until you are spoken to.</font>

38:08.000 --> 38:10.760
That's a system I am familiar with.

38:19.120 --> 38:21.160
<font color="#ffff00">Now I'm here, I'm a little nervous.</font>

38:21.200 --> 38:22.640
<font color="#00ffff">Perfectly natural, sir.</font>

38:23.760 --> 38:26.600
<font color="#ffff00">If I see Victoria,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I will not stumble.</font>

38:32.240 --> 38:34.240
(Door squeaks open)

38:42.880 --> 38:46.320
<font color="#00ffff">Miss Mott and Miss Cabot,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">from Boston,</font>

38:46.360 --> 38:49.000
<font color="#00ffff">and this is Mr Barrett,</font>

38:49.040 --> 38:53.680
<font color="#00ffff">who was a slave in Virginia</font>
<font color="#00ffff">until he made a most valiant escape.</font>

38:54.480 --> 38:57.160
<font color="#ffff00">Was your escape very difficult,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Mr Barrett?</font>

38:58.160 --> 39:02.840
Once I got away from the bloodhounds
it became a little easier.

39:04.920 --> 39:07.800
But I didn't mind the hardships

39:07.840 --> 39:13.800
because I knew I was on the way
to freedom, thank the Lord.

39:16.680 --> 39:18.320
<font color="#ffff00">It is good that you are here today.</font>

39:18.360 --> 39:21.680
And it is good that you're here
today...

39:25.280 --> 39:26.840
..sir.

39:26.880 --> 39:29.240
<font color="#ffff00">I'm glad to be of some use.</font>

39:29.280 --> 39:31.280
<font color="#ffff00">Please.</font>

39:38.080 --> 39:40.280
I hope I am not late.
<font color="#00ffff">No, Ma'am.</font>

39:40.320 --> 39:42.000
<font color="#00ffff">The proceedings have not yet begun.</font>

39:42.040 --> 39:46.920
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Buxton has asked me to apologise</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in advance for not having organised</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a Royal box.</font>

39:46.960 --> 39:49.200
<font color="#00ffff">But I assured him</font>
<font color="#00ffff">that you would not mind.</font>

39:49.240 --> 39:51.560
I have come incognito.

39:51.600 --> 39:55.040
<font color="#00ffff">Forgive me, Ma'am, but your disguise</font>
<font color="#00ffff">is not impenetrable.</font>

39:55.080 --> 39:57.280
<font color="#00ffff">You will be the cynosure</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of all eyes.</font>

40:00.920 --> 40:05.360
Do you know, Lehzen... I find I am
feeling a little faint.

40:05.400 --> 40:07.320
<font color="#00ff00">Faint, Majesty?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Yes.</font>

40:07.360 --> 40:09.480
Faint.

40:10.080 --> 40:11.880
I think I shall return to the palace.

40:11.920 --> 40:14.480
<font color="#00ffff">I think that is a wise decision,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Ma'am.</font>

40:17.760 --> 40:19.880
Anson...

40:20.920 --> 40:24.000
..don't tell the Prince
until afterwards.

40:24.040 --> 40:26.040
I don't want him to be distracted.

40:26.080 --> 40:28.320
<font color="#00ffff">Understood, Ma'am.</font>

40:42.240 --> 40:44.680
<font color="#00ff00">His Royal Highness Prince Albert.</font>

41:05.440 --> 41:07.440
<font color="#ffff00">(Clears throat)</font>

41:17.880 --> 41:21.960
<font color="#ffff00">As President of the British And</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Foreign Anti-Slavery Society...</font>

41:23.560 --> 41:26.240
<font color="#ffff00">..I am glad to see</font>
<font color="#ffff00">so many people here.</font>

41:30.720 --> 41:32.560
<font color="#ffff00">This...</font>

41:49.880 --> 41:55.920
<font color="#ffff00">This barbarous trade is repugnant</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to Christianity</font>

41:55.960 --> 41:59.960
<font color="#ffff00">and the blackest stain</font>
<font color="#ffff00">upon civilised Europe.</font>

42:00.000 --> 42:04.360
<font color="#ffff00">Mankind, born and brought up</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in a civilised society...</font>

42:04.400 --> 42:07.600
<font color="#ffff00">are physically and morally</font>
<font color="#ffff00">speaking...</font>

42:07.640 --> 42:09.920
<font color="#ffff00">..to preside over the meeting of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">this Society</font>

42:09.960 --> 42:13.840
<font color="#ffff00">from a conviction of its paramount</font>
<font color="#ffff00">importance to the great interests of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">humanity...</font>

42:13.880 --> 42:15.840
<font color="#ffff00">..persevering exertions of England</font>

42:15.880 --> 42:18.960
<font color="#ffff00">to abolish that atrocious traffic</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in human beings</font>

42:19.000 --> 42:21.520
<font color="#ffff00">have not, as yet, led to...</font>

42:21.560 --> 42:24.320
<font color="#ffff00">..this great country will not relax</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in its efforts</font>

42:24.360 --> 42:27.680
<font color="#ffff00">until it has finally, and forever,</font>

42:27.720 --> 42:29.600
<font color="#ffff00">put an end to a state of things...</font>

42:29.640 --> 42:34.920
<font color="#ffff00">..therefore trust that Providence</font>
<font color="#ffff00">will prosper our exertions</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in so holy a cause,</font>

42:34.960 --> 42:37.160
<font color="#ffff00">and that we may, at no distant</font>
<font color="#ffff00">period,</font>

42:37.200 --> 42:42.200
<font color="#ffff00">be rewarded by the accomplishment of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the great and humane object</font>

42:42.240 --> 42:46.880
<font color="#ffff00">for the promotion of which</font>
<font color="#ffff00">we have this day met.</font>

42:49.840 --> 42:51.840
<font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font>

43:21.280 --> 43:23.840
I must congratulate you, sir.

43:23.880 --> 43:25.400
That was a fine speech.

43:25.440 --> 43:27.000
<font color="#ffff00">Thank you, Sir Robert.</font>

43:27.880 --> 43:30.600
<font color="#ffff00">This time, it seems,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">we are on the same side.</font>

43:46.000 --> 43:48.320
How did your speech go?

43:49.120 --> 43:51.400
<font color="#ffff00">I think it was well received.</font>

43:51.440 --> 43:53.760
<font color="#ffff00">I wish you had been there</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to hear me.</font>

43:59.160 --> 44:01.280
This was your victory, my angel...

44:03.360 --> 44:05.120
..not mine.

44:08.680 --> 44:10.680
<font color="#ffff00">You're not tired any more?</font>

44:12.240 --> 44:14.240
No.

44:15.320 --> 44:17.320
Not at all.

44:49.440 --> 44:52.480
..five, six, seven, eight, nine, ten.

44:52.520 --> 44:58.240
One, two, three, four, five, six,
seven, eight, nine, ten.

44:58.280 --> 45:02.960
One, two, three, four, five, six,
seven, eight...

45:03.000 --> 45:05.000
<font color="#ffff00">What are you doing?</font>

45:07.360 --> 45:09.360
N-Nothing.

45:12.480 --> 45:14.800
<font color="#ffff00">Did someone tell you to do this?</font>

45:16.640 --> 45:18.800
Lehzen said if I...

45:18.840 --> 45:21.280
didn't want to have children
right away...

45:22.920 --> 45:27.200
Of course I want children.
Your children, Albert.

45:30.200 --> 45:32.200
Just...

45:34.120 --> 45:35.640
..not yet.

45:36.520 --> 45:38.520
<font color="#ffff00">You know, Lehzen is misinformed.</font>

45:41.880 --> 45:44.920
<font color="#ffff00">The only way to avoid conception is</font>
<font color="#ffff00">erm...</font>

45:48.320 --> 45:50.240
<font color="#ffff00">..abstinence.</font>

45:50.280 --> 45:54.680
<font color="#ffff00">Is that what you want, Victoria?</font>

45:56.600 --> 45:58.600
<font color="#ffff00">Abstinence?</font>

46:13.960 --> 46:17.440
<font color="#00ff00">It is incumbent upon Your Majesty</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to nominate a Regent.</font>

46:17.480 --> 46:22.160
Your Queen is sick.
<font color="#00ffff">WELLINGTON: If the Queen dies,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">are we to be ruled by a German?</font>

46:22.200 --> 46:24.960
<font color="#ffff00">HARRIET: Chillington Hall is well</font>
<font color="#ffff00">situated for your research.</font>

46:25.000 --> 46:27.440
May I ask where you stand
on the matter of the regency?

46:28.160 --> 46:29.440
<font color="#00ffff">(Giggles)</font>

46:29.480 --> 46:32.200
<font color="#ffff00">I do not hunt. I shoot.</font>

46:32.240 --> 46:33.960
If I wish to bring railways or
anything

46:34.000 --> 46:36.920
to the attention of the English
people, then I shall do it myself!

46:36.960 --> 46:39.840
<font color="#ffff00">This is the future!</font>
